item.title: My 4th Picture/ Sig Using PS CS2
item.dc:creator: @kaza Kaza
item.description:
@kaza wrote:

If you having problems with size, if you make the sig, then think, oh crap, this is going to look silly, then go to : Image > Canvas Size > **px x **px.

And, woot my tut ftw ;), and this is okay for a 4th, your starting to learn the basics of photoshop, good job, although it is still pretty basic.

I would recomend making the size smaller, and if you have a smaller sig, stick with 1 render that blends with the bg.

Read some more tutorials, maybe download some brushes because they easy to use, and are good for people starting photoshop.

Anyway, 4/10.

Read full topic
